snippet.title: TS2019 UK Edition - OUT NOW
snippet.description:
ESRB Rating: Everyone

Train Simulator 2019 is now out and in addition we've thrown together a bundle for our UK fans. The UK Edition includes everything contained in TS19 as well as the Woodhead Electric Railway in Blue Route Add-On!

Thanks for checking out our videos! There’s tonnes more on our channel, or keep up with the news by following us on the links below:

www.facebook.com/railsimulator
www.twitter.com/railsimulator
www.forums.dovetailgames.com
